The SIFAX Group management team recently embarked on a retreat. The retreat provided all participants with insights on how the company will achieve its five year strategic plan and their role as staff. It was attended by all managers in the Group. L-R: Adekunle Oyinloye, Group Managing Director, SIFAX Group; John Jenkins, Managing Director, Ports & Cargo Handling Services Limited, a subsidiary of SIFAX Group; Capt. Ibraheem Olugbade, Executive Director, SIFAX Off Dock and Tunji Olusinde, Executive Director, Legal Services/Company Secretary at the 2020 SIFAX Group management retreat held at the Landmark Event Centre, Lagos. L-R: Adekunle Oyinloye, Group Managing Director, SIFAX Group; John Jenkins, Managing Director, Ports & Cargo Handling Services Limited; Capt. Ibraheem Olugbade, Executive Director, SIFAX Off Dock and Kayode Ogunwole, General Manager, IT, SIFAX Group at the SIFAX Group management retreat held at the Landmark Event Centre, Lagos.  Various speakers including Mr. Soji Oyawoye, a renowned HR consultant and Lanre Olusola, Nigeriaâ€™s foremost business coach took participants through various sessions on strategy, sales & marketing and nutrition & health.